<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ethers.js Tutorial</title>
    <!-- Import the ethers.js library -->
    <script src="https://cdn.ethers.io/lib/ethers-5.2.umd.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Include MetaMask script -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@metamask/detect-provider@1.2.0/dist/index.js"></script>
    
    <style>
        header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px;
    background-color: #f8f8f8;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
}

#logo {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

nav ul li {
    margin-left: 20px;
}

nav ul li button {
    padding: 5px 15px;
    cursor: pointer;
}


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div id="logo">Logo</div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/play">Play</a></li>
                <li><a href="/earn">Earn</a></li>
                <!-- The button id is used for the JavaScript connection functionality -->
                <li><button id="connectButton">Connect Wallet</button></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <h1>Ethers.js Cheat Sheet Tutorial</h1>
    <p>Learn how to interact with the Ethereum blockchain using ethers.js and MetaMask.</p>



    <!-- Dynamic content will be displayed here -->
    <div id="content"></div>

        <!-- Import the MetaMask connect script -->
        <script src="./js/metamask_connect_script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
